673
00:42:45,110 --> 00:42:47,926
- Well, we were supposed to
have a picnic, but the rain.

674
00:42:47,926 --> 00:42:50,080
- (laughs) Isn't that always the way?

675
00:42:50,080 --> 00:42:51,490
