676
00:42:51,490 --> 00:42:53,573
- Okay, that'll be five cents please.

677
00:42:54,865 --> 00:42:56,350
- There you go.
- Thank you so much.

678
00:42:56,350 --> 00:42:57,510
Here you are.
- Have a good day.

679
00:42:57,510 --> 00:42:58,446
- You too.

680
00:42:58,446 --> 00:43:01,196
