780
00:47:45,992 --> 00:47:47,620
- Hey, he needs a doctor, quickly.

781
00:47:47,620 --> 00:47:49,970
- [Man] Uh, I can take
him, follow me, come on!

782
00:47:51,030 --> 00:47:52,016
- Careful, careful.

783
00:47:52,016 --> 00:47:55,320
